<h1>Welcome</h1>

<p>
    The theme picker above resolves its initial theme from a
    server-side cookie. When you choose a new theme, the client.js
    posts to <code>/api/theme</code>, which sets the cookie. The
    next request paints with the new theme from byte one.
</p>

<p>
    For details see <a href="../../docs/ssr.md">docs/ssr.md</a>.
</p>
